            <p class="text-gray-600">探索农村心血管病风险管理的创新模式</p>
        </div>

        <div class="glassmorphism p-6 mb-8">
            <div class="waveform mb-4" style="background-image: url('https://s.coze.cn/image/eQSczaAh2SM/')"></div>
            
